<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.9.1">
<l>māṉēy nōkkunallīr vaikalumviṉai yēṉmeliya</l>
<l>vāṉār vaṇkamuku matumallikai yuṅkamaḻun</l>
<l>tēṉār cōlaikaḷcūḻ tiruvalla vāḻuṟaiyuṅ</l>
<l>kōṉā raiyaṭiyē ṇaṭikūṭuva teṉṟukolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You good ones with doe-like glances, as I with [bad] Karma weaken daily,</l>
<l>when will there be joining [his] feet for me [who is] servant of the king</l>
<l>who dwells at Tiruvallavāḻ surrounded by groves full of honey,</l>
<l>where lucious Areca palms up to the sky and honey jasmine spread fragrance?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
